window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Welcome back, friends. Get comfortable, grab a drink, light the fire in your hearth….</p> <p>This is the story of how I, the one and only Shady Greg, saved the world of Jadera.</p> <p>What, you thought it was over after my Misty Isle adventures? To tell you the truth, so did I. After everything, I really thought I could run Greg’s Dungeon Emporium and rest on my laurels.</p> <p>Unfortunately for me—and luckily for you—Jadera and more specifically, The Profit, hate it when I’m not scrabbling for my life and gold.</p> <p>So settle in, friends, as I recount the tale of my life…and death.</p> <p>The final chapter in the story of my life awaits you. Won’t you join me?</p>"; 
